1
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:30,969
(Moonlit Reunion)

2
00:01:31,050 --> 00:01:33,920
(Episode 17)

3
00:01:34,008 --> 00:01:36,760
(Mei Residence)

4
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,325
Loach.

5
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:47,880
I am not a loach.

6
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,560
I bought you fried loach anyway.

7
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,286
White Serpent told me

8
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:57,520
a small demon needs to eat its kind to recover.

9
00:01:59,703 --> 00:02:00,960
It is as big as you.

10
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,245
How do you eat it?

11
00:02:02,818 --> 00:02:05,000
I don't care. Deal with it yourself.

12
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,160
How many times do I have to tell you?

13
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,798
I am a Black Snake!

14
00:02:11,878 --> 00:02:13,560
Yes. Forget it if you don't want it.

15
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,200
I'll eat it instead.

16
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,765
This is premium ink.

17
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,325
Thankfully, you didn't break it.

18
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:36,765
Premium ink like this is suitable for drawing.

19
00:02:37,038 --> 00:02:39,325
I'm going to draw an illustration book of demons

20
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:40,679
for Lady Liu

21
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:41,925
as a gift.

22
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,645
The demons you know

23
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,765
all come from the "Compendium of Demons" on the table.

24
00:02:48,439 --> 00:02:49,966
Everything has been recorded.

25
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,045
What else can you draw?

26
00:02:52,422 --> 00:02:55,433
You are just copying and adding some elements.

27
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,526
You know nothing.

28
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,839
This is the most complete book

29
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,406
that has records of demons.

30
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,846
You see me, a Black Snake, as a loach.

31
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,806
It's obvious that this book isn't good.

32
00:03:06,144 --> 00:03:09,831
- You...   - Demons are nurtured by Heaven and Earth.

33
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,205
It has many varieties.

34
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:13,799
There are still many kinds

35
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:16,165
that mortals haven't heard of or seen before.

36
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:18,325
Unlike a big demon like me.

37
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,485
You are a big demon?

38
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:25,120
You must be knowledgeable and know everything.

39
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,765
I don't want you to keep asking me questions. It's annoying.

40
00:03:28,671 --> 00:03:31,205
I'll just tell you some stories

41
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:34,205
to repay you for taking care of me.

42
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,519
Sure. Tell me slowly.

43
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,045
I'll draw them while you tell me.

44
00:04:10,952 --> 00:04:12,637
Tigers are the kings of the mountains.

45
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,566
Today, I will tell you

46
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:18,166
about a tiger demon that gained its form after cultivating for 1,000 years.

47
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:24,046
The tiger has saw-like teeth and a fierce glare.

48
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,405
It cultivates fire spells

49
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:28,366
so there's a fire mark on its forehead.

50
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,006
It is three feet tall.

51
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:35,486
When its powers grow, it can turn into a demon that's eight feet tall.

52
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,885
When does its power grow?

53
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:41,445
When its Life Gate,

54
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,726
the area between its eyebrows, is attacked.

55
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,885
I see.

56
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,445
How is it going?

57
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,879
The mighty Tiger Demon

58
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:08,606
that dominates a mountain

59
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:10,799
appeared like this in your drawing?

60
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,285
Overall, it still looks good.

61
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,046
It's special.

62
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,525
What do you think?

63
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,765
It's not bad.

64
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,645
It's lifelike.

65
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:40,765
No wonder I think the ink is weird.

66
00:06:41,279 --> 00:06:42,965
It actually contains an evil spell.

67
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,006
It can cause trouble for Demon City now.

68
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,046
This is bad.

69
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,085
It doesn't have a demon core?

70
00:08:36,975 --> 00:08:40,709
(Duke Wu's Residence)

71
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,846
Brother Mei!

72
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:02,405
I haven't seen you in the Arcane Appraisal Bureau recently.

73
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,446
I've heard many rumors.

74
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:09,126
I don't even know

75
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:11,246
which of them is true.

76
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,565
What did you hear?

77
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,885
People are talking in the city.

78
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:22,885
Sometimes,

79
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:26,405
they say you were chased out of Chang'an by Princess Qinghe.

80
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:31,726
Sometimes, they say Princess Qinghe has a new man.

81
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:33,920
Sometimes, they also say

82
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:37,446
there are two men who volunteer to stay in this residence.

83
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,880
They appear like melons in the summer.

84
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,606
One after another.

85
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:43,446
Round after round.

86
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,045
Before I could comprehend the previous stories,

87
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,206
well,

88
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:49,565
I heard news about the Grand Aromatics Competition.

89
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,885
They say the powerful Mr. Mei

90
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,246
saved the princess.

91
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:55,645
When I think about it,

92
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,246
someone as excellent,

93
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,285
must not be Fourth Master Mei.

94
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:04,326
Enough. Stop talking.

95
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,006
Why are you looking for me so early in the morning?

96
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,246
Something's wrong.

97
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,645
Something serious.

98
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:30,525
Mr. Mei, this case is a little troublesome indeed.

99
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,726
This...

100
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,925
These are...

101
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,006
Little Loach!

102
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:51,726
What is it?

103
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:54,326
The whole place is stained with blood.

104
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,925
It turns into ink?

105
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:03,606
There's no blood.

106
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:06,246
You probably made a mistake because you didn't sleep well.

107
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,846
Little Loach, look at my painting.

108
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:12,000
The Tiger Demon's ink has become pale.

109
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,006
Perhaps you didn't grind your ink well.

110
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,157
Impossible. I've ground ink since I was young.

111
00:12:16,235 --> 00:12:17,559
There's no problem with the ink.

112
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,880
Are you questioning me?

113
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,966
I...

114
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,606
I'm not.

115
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:24,925
Do you still want to hear stories about other demons?

116
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:33,285
I do.

117
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,120
Today, we'll be talking about

118
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:40,925
the legendary Pomegranate Demon, Pi Ning.

119
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,966
Its head was a pomegranate.

120
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:49,405
However, it pretends to be a pretty girl during the day.

121
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,525
It uses its long hair to cover its head.

122
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:55,885
When it fights, it shakes its head violently

123
00:12:56,039 --> 00:12:57,405
and shake its hair away.

124
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:02,640
The countless pomegranate seeds

125
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,805
are used as darts.

126
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:06,206
They are the best throwing weapon.

127
00:13:09,727 --> 00:13:11,812
It shakes its head while fighting?

128
00:13:12,559 --> 00:13:15,165
Little Loach, are you not lying to me?

129
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,486
Why would I lie to you?

130
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,920
It looks like that thing in the mortal realm.

131
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,525
What is it again?

132
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,846
Rattle drum.

133
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:39,486
I also fought a Deer Demon once.

134
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:42,719
Its eyes grew on its back.

135
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:44,565
The eyes looked everywhere

136
00:13:44,967 --> 00:13:46,572
and could see everything.

137
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:50,045
The four antlers on its head were very sharp.

138
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:53,486
I heard it likes to rub its antlers on poisonous tree bark.

139
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,966
After a long time,

140
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,925
its antlers became extremely poisonous

141
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,846
with poison that was hard to cure.

142
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,565
In this world,

143
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:08,206
plants and animals aren't the only things that can demonify.

144
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:10,565
When an object comes in contact with blood,

145
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:12,606
it can kill as well.

146
00:14:14,216 --> 00:14:15,255
There's a demon

147
00:14:15,336 --> 00:14:19,263
that is born from a jade die of a gambling den.

148
00:14:19,759 --> 00:14:21,006
One day,

149
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:24,325
someone lost a lot of money in the gambling den

150
00:14:24,405 --> 00:14:26,119
and started swinging his blade and killing people.

151
00:14:26,985 --> 00:14:29,285
Blood splattered on the die

152
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,126
and it became evil.

153
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,846
The Die Devil might be small

154
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:35,765
but it is very cruel.

155
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:39,839
Its six sides have 21 eyes in total

156
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,446
and every eye is blood red.

157
00:14:42,399 --> 00:14:45,366
The more blood it sees, the more it gets excited.

158
00:14:46,519 --> 00:14:49,446
I remember a temple

159
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:51,165
that has been abandoned for many years.

160
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:54,405
There's a broken water jar in the yard.

161
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,086
It cannot hold water

162
00:14:57,639 --> 00:15:00,160
but it moves with the wind through its cracks

163
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:04,885
and uses the wind as its attacks.

164
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:12,045
The sky is full of stars but the moon cannot be seen.

165
00:15:12,759 --> 00:15:15,685
There are many mysterious incidents on land.

166
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:19,206
Last night,

167
00:15:19,519 --> 00:15:21,880
a demon appeared in Chang'an.

168
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,920
It has the form of smoke and ink

169
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:26,446
and it can change into many shapes.

170
00:15:30,519 --> 00:15:33,925
It seems like the people of Chang'an will be terrified now.

171
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:40,846
Have you heard? There are demons in Chang'an.

172
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,405
The wine seller said it was a Pig Demon.

173
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,640
Nonsense. It was a Fox Demon.

174
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,880
Excuse me. Where did you hear

175
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,285
the stories of demons?

176
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:50,925
Many people are talking about it in the city.

177
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:53,126
- Let's go.   - Who are you calling a pig?

178
00:15:53,351 --> 00:15:54,719
You are a flying pig.

179
00:15:54,799 --> 00:15:56,086
Everyone in your family is a pig.

180
00:15:57,720 --> 00:16:00,045
Brother Mei, what were you talking about?

181
00:16:03,039 --> 00:16:04,765
Many people in Chang'an

182
00:16:04,991 --> 00:16:06,679
have started talking about the demons.

183
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:07,765
No way.

184
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,525
We have been ordering the people

185
00:16:10,679 --> 00:16:11,966
not to tell other people

186
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,805
to prevent them from panicking.

187
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,525
News of it has spread so much in less than a day.

188
00:16:17,879 --> 00:16:19,846
This isn't just a simple rumor.

189
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,846
Brother Mei, are you saying

190
00:16:23,519 --> 00:16:25,645
that someone is fueling the rumors?

191
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,366
It's possible.

192
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:30,640
Brother Mei, do you want me

193
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,366
to check the registration of the ink shop?

194
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:36,405
The key to the traces is ink.

195
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,685
The power of the ink isn't a kind of demonic power

196
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:41,685
but a kind of evil spell indeed.

197
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,846
Evil spell?

198
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,565
What is it?

199
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:49,486
Have you heard about the suppression technique?

200
00:16:50,159 --> 00:16:51,165
No.

201
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,959
Simply speaking, it's an illegal spell.

202
00:16:54,039 --> 00:16:56,079
The spell caster doesn't learn it from cultivation

203
00:16:56,159 --> 00:16:59,045
but from sacrificing his own body.

204
00:16:59,279 --> 00:17:03,405
Brother Mei, how do you know it's the suppression technique?

205
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,565
Right.

206
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:07,759
Every demon will turn into its original form after dying.

207
00:17:07,839 --> 00:17:09,605
It will never vanish for no reason.

208
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:12,045
If there's no body, it's not a demon.

209
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,686
That's how suppression technique works.

210
00:17:14,079 --> 00:17:15,640
They assimilate their conscience

211
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,166
into an external object

212
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,646
to achieve the goal of controlling that object.

213
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,560
The traces left behind by the tiger's death

214
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,406
are the manifestation of the suppression technique.

215
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,686
I see.

216
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,966
Can I have it now?

217
00:17:30,799 --> 00:17:31,805
Here you go.

218
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:38,006
How do we investigate the spell caster?

219
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:40,166
Should we start from the ink shop?

220
00:17:41,559 --> 00:17:43,926
Right now, we can only use this stupid method.

221
00:17:45,015 --> 00:17:47,000
(Ink Workshop)

222
00:17:52,322 --> 00:17:54,126
The Arcane Appraisal Bureau is investigating a case.

223
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,726
Please show me your ledger.

224
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:02,080
The ledger is my shop's secret.

225
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:04,365
Your bureau can't...

226
00:18:05,759 --> 00:18:08,045
Sure. Please come with me.

227
00:18:10,519 --> 00:18:12,605
The Arcane Appraisal Bureau? I don't want to go there.

228
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:14,325
I'll show it to you. Please wait.

229
00:18:19,079 --> 00:18:20,085
Please take a look.

230
00:18:38,367 --> 00:18:40,508
(Purchased by Fourth Master Mei)

231
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,006
Take care.

232
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,166
Boss.

233
00:19:04,319 --> 00:19:06,720
Show me the ledger that you showed him just now.

234
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,246
Which bureau are you from?

235
00:19:10,799 --> 00:19:12,479
My ledger isn't anything special.

236
00:19:12,559 --> 00:19:14,120
Why is everyone trying to look at it?

237
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,206
Move!

238
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,246
Here you go.

239
00:19:21,519 --> 00:19:23,325
Take your time.

240
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,845
This one.

