Fourth Brother!

248
00:19:52,359 --> 00:19:54,926
(The Ink Demons in Chang'an actually came from these paintings.)

249
00:20:02,079 --> 00:20:03,085
Fourth Brother!

250
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,486
Get up!

251
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,926
Enough! Get up!

252
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,486
Fourth Brother!

253
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:12,605
Come!

254
00:20:24,727 --> 00:20:26,059
- Move!   - Stop!

255
00:20:26,143 --> 00:20:27,507
Don't come near if you want to save him!

256
00:21:16,599 --> 00:21:17,646
Fourth Master!

257
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,886
How are you?

258
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,166
Little Fish?

259
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,006
Are you awake now?

260
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,206
Why am I here?

261
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,246
What happened to me?

262
00:21:57,599 --> 00:21:59,446
Why did you kick the table for no reason?

263
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:02,045
No. It wasn't me.

264
00:22:02,799 --> 00:22:05,246
Didn't you see something pass by?

265
00:22:06,039 --> 00:22:07,045
What?

266
00:22:07,759 --> 00:22:09,006
You must have made a mistake.

267
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,246
I'm talking to you.

268
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,446
What are you looking at?

269
00:22:20,119 --> 00:22:21,686
I'm not in the sky.

270
00:22:22,119 --> 00:22:23,525
Why are you looking at the sky?

271
00:22:23,717 --> 00:22:24,941
What did you say?

272
00:22:26,519 --> 00:22:27,726
I want to ask you

273
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:31,406
who you like

274
00:22:31,799 --> 00:22:33,085
between Mr. Mei and Mr. Pei.

275
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,800
You purposely summoned me into the palace

276
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,279
just to talk about this?

277
00:22:37,359 --> 00:22:38,805
Mr. Mei

278
